dct_title_s: NUOVA CARTA DEL POLO ARTICO secondo l'ultime osservazioni
dct_description_sm: [1740?], with Italian place names. Named California places are: C. Blanco, C.Mendocin, P. S. Francis, and S. Barbera F.

Issued in: Atlante novissimo che contiene tutte le parti del mondo, nel quale sono esattamente descritti gl' imperj, le monarchie, stati, republiche, ec. ... , [V.1, no.21]/ G. Delisle. -- Venezia: G. Albrizzi Q. Girol., 1740-1750.
Northern part of California shown, with rounded northern coast. Mozeemlek Country to its north, with suggestion of a strait and land to northwest.
LC 594 and 600; Nordenskiöld (p.250, Plate 118); Nordenskiöld Collection 1,64(21); UCB.
Title on banderole at top of map.
